messages.title: TOMORROW OUR NHS NEEDS YOU.
messages.content: Stay at home or voting for any other party will let the Tories do this: Cut 8000000 nurse's hours, Spend 12000000 on leaflets promoting NHS privatisation.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Labour commits to preserving the NHS by reversing cuts to nurse's hours and opposing the privatisation efforts.
